Flow layout
--> flowlayout implements a simlpe layout style,which is familiar to how 
words flow in a text editor
-->the direction of the layout is governed by the container's component 
orientation property,which by default ,is left to right, top to buttom
-->therfore by default components are laid out line-by-line beginning at the upper-left corner
--> in all cases when a line is filled ,layout advances to next line
-->a small space is left between each compenent ,above and below as well as left and right